cs.HC, cs.GR, cs.CV, cs.AR, cs.MM

This paper discusses the technical challenges and potential applications of augmented reality and virtual reality, which are related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC), computer graphics (cs.GR), computer vision (cs.CV), augmented reality (cs.AR), and multimedia (cs.MM). The practical evaluation of Microsoft HoloLens also suggests a focus on human-computer interaction and augmented reality. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely to be relevant to this paper.
